parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly, leading to injuries or accidents, or fail to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The SRS light illuminates on the dashboard
airbags deploy unexpectedly
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
the vehicle's anti-lock braking system (ABS) is disabled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the SRS warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which may lead to unexpected airbag deployment or failure to deploy in a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The SRS light illuminates on the dashboard
airbags may deploy unexpectedly
airbags may fail to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly, leading to injuries or accidents, or fail to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The SRS light illuminates on the dashboard
airbags deploy unexpectedly
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
the vehicle's anti-lock braking system (ABS) is disabled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS modulator can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The ABS light comes on
the brakes feel spongy or mushy
the brakes pulsate
the vehicle skids or loses control when braking
the ABS system leaks fluid
the master cylinder needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power or stall, leading to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The transmission jumps or makes a loud noise when shifting
the vehicle bangs into gear
the speed and powertrain are unknown.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause the vehicle to lose control or crash, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The brakes fail to stop the vehicle
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the brakes pulsate or vibrate
the vehicle collides with another vehicle or object.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The fuel gauge does not work
the fuel lines leak
the fuel system needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the engine to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails to start
the dashboard lights and power windows fail to operate
the key gets stuck in the ignition
the ignition switch feels loose or worn out
the engine shuts down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various electrical components to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The dashboard lights
gear shift indicator
and clock display fail to light or operate intermittently
the radio and power windows fail to operate
the SRS light illuminates constantly
the interior lights and sunvisor light fail to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter motor can cause the engine to fail to start or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The starter motor engages while the key is not in the car
the engine starts to smoke
the starter and cables catch fire.
